events.text:
Hana tries to stab him with her makeshift knife keychain, but Shinji avoids it.
They both tussle for a bit, but Hana's strength overwhelms Shinji immensely.
Feeling cornered, he climbs onto a chair and tells her to stay back. 
The chair was right in front of an open window,
so Hana simply smiled...
and pushed his body out of it.
Shinji loses his footing, felt the cool breeze of the evening wind...
and plummets to his death.

Aw, that ended too fast.
Crap, I left behind quite a mess here...
No time to think about that now, I need to act shocked and fool my friends.
Well then,
[speed=4][b]Let Hana's Facade begin.[b]
